            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Coelia Pieris <lb n="2"/><abbr>M</abbr> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Choelia <note>sic</note> Pieris <lb n="2"/><abbr>M</abbr> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Anhänger in Form einer tabula ansata; Inschrift auf Vorder- und Rückseite. Z. 2: Für M verschiedene Auflösungen möglich: M(arti), M(ercurio), M(inerviae), m(emor). Wiedergabe von Coelia auf der 2. Seite als Choeliae.</p>
            </div>
